---
title: Creamy Miso Mushroom Rigatoni and Chicken Breast with Spinach, Cheese and Chives
description: A customer favourite, this Creamy Miso Mushroom and Chicken Breast Rigatoni is a tried-and-tested recipe that always wins with a crowd.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R40_W30_UK_QV13339-20_Main_add_low-848eb580.jpg
